               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17900526-2-cd8" type="crimeDate">12th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-2-off7 t17900526-2-cd8"></join> last, eight shirts, value 2 l. five pair of silk stockings, value 10 s. three pair of nankeen breeches, value 20 s. three child's shirts, value 3 s. the property of Sir 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900526-2-victim53" type="victimName">
                           James 
